longBusinessSummary: Beyond Medical Technologies Inc., an industrial/technology company, develops waste digester systems for food and pharmaceuticals industries in Canada. Its Organivore and Pharmavore waste digester systems turns organic waste into clean water. The company also engages in the manufacturing and distribution of personal protective equipment, including medical grade face masks. In addition, it offers health communications platform that facilitates doctors to streamline communications with their patients and remotely monitor them. The company was formerly known as Micron Waste Technologies Inc. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
